N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 81.6 - Rule inapplicable to governmental agency

State Regulations

This Part shall not apply to any license or permit issued
to any department, board, commission or other agency of the State or to any
political subdivision of the State. Notes
